NAME
    edit-symlink

DESCRIPTION
    Workaround to update existing symlink target path (since technically they can't be edited)

    This function requires two parameters...
        @1 = Name of symbolic link to edit
        @2 = Full destination path to update existing symlink with

SYNOPSIS
    edit-symlink EXISTING_LINK TARGET_PATH

EXAMPLES
    edit-symlink ./existing-directory-symlink /home/user/new-directory

AVAILABLE OPTIONS:
    N/A
